entries.femaleVariant: The fuck you want?
This a fight club?
Looking for Logan Garcia.
You look familiar...
Hey... You look familiar. You're from Watson, right? Didn't your old man work in Salman's garage?
Yeah. 'Fore they tossed him in the joint.
Forget it. Doin' that won't end well for you.
Nah, it's a dentist's office. Unless you want your skull drilled, I'd move along.
Yeah. For Animals.
Used to be a factory for manufacturing paints or some shit. Put in some equipment, slap a ring in the middle – got yourself a kennel.
Lookin' for trouble, huh? 'Cause Logan'll guarantee it.
Here for a fight.
Here for a fight.
You? Interesting...
Why, "interesting"?
Wondering if I'll recognize you after.
Lookin' for Logan Garcia.
This is a fight club, right?
Right, I remember. Badges caught him kleppin' watches?
Among other things. Peeps dying on the streets like flies and all they cared about were stolen hubcaps. Fucking narcs.
Anyway – you wanted something?
If he's not in the ring, he's upstairs in his office. Just don't go in unless you want your face realigned.
